WEBVTT

00:00:00.783 --> 00:00:05.334
UNK SHTAYIM CIPI KICHLER MERAYENET ET HUGO FISHMAN.

00:00:07.170 --> 00:00:08.610
nu, azoy hob ikh

00:00:08.610 --> 00:00:12.330
gegangen in kheyder in Siget,

00:00:12.810 --> 00:00:21.390
un ge- gelernt, ikh hob ober gevolt geyn in shul oykhet, dort ober hob ikh shoyn nisht gekent geyn in shul, vayl in Rozavlye bin ikh geblibn mit dray klasn.

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:23.060
dray klasn shul.

00:00:23.396 --> 00:00:26.161
yetst az du fartseylst fun Siget, yo?

00:00:26.161 --> 00:00:29.415
Siget, in velkhn yor bistu gekumen keyn Siget?

00:00:28.430 --> 00:00:31.370
in toyznt nayn hundert naynem un tsvontsik.

00:00:31.520 --> 00:00:32.980
ende yor.

00:00:33.160 --> 00:00:34.520
ze'mir ongekumen keyn Siget.

00:00:34.520 --> 00:00:36.220
ikh bin gegangen in kheyder,

00:00:36.220 --> 00:00:38.950
vi azoy ikh hob dertseylt, dort ongehoybn tsu arbetn oyf,

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:40.270
vi ikh hob gekent.

00:00:40.270 --> 00:00:44.190
bay dem bir fabrik, bay yenem mit di shtrikn.

00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:49.500
un gesh- mayne shvester hobn gearbet,

00:00:49.500 --> 00:00:54.920
se iz gegangen ales. vos git ober got in aza tsayt?

00:00:55.170 --> 00:00:58.120
di groyse shvester vert krank.

00:00:58.620 --> 00:01:02.290
deroyf oyf a yor, anderthalbn vi undz ze'mir arayngekumen

00:01:02.310 --> 00:01:03.880
in shtot voynen.

00:01:04.520 --> 00:01:08.790
zi hot zikh bashtetikt, zi hot zikh ibergehoybn.

00:01:08.920 --> 00:01:11.000
un se hot zikh ir gerisn epes.

00:01:11.930 --> 00:01:15.830
un deye hot gemuzt lign, iz gelign,

00:01:15.960 --> 00:01:19.210
un se iz aroysgeblibn, vi azoy me zogt, a shtikl broyt.

00:01:19.210 --> 00:01:21.430
a fardiner in der shtub.

00:01:22.230 --> 00:01:24.310
un s'iz geven,

00:01:24.730 --> 00:01:27.680
shver, nokh shtar- shverer di lage,

00:01:28.270 --> 00:01:32.870
un mayn mame hot gehat a shvester in Amerike.

00:01:32.870 --> 00:01:34.600
Sore hot zi geheysn.

00:01:34.910 --> 00:01:38.720
yene fleg alts shikn, azoy eyn mol in a monat,

00:01:38.720 --> 00:01:40.600
eyn mol in anderthalbn monat,

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.150
fleg zi shikn,

00:01:42.150 --> 00:01:44.140
ikh veys, a hundert daler,

00:01:44.670 --> 00:01:47.310
ikh veys vifl mer pinktlekh veys ikh nisht,

00:01:47.330 --> 00:01:50.760
nu, un deys hot oykhet aroysgeholfn tsum lebn.

00:01:51.150 --> 00:01:59.530
nu, in der tsayt, mayne shvester zenen shoyn gevorn gresere meydlekh, azoy, un hot shoyn ongehoybn yinglekh

00:01:59.610 --> 00:02:02.490
tsu hoyfirn, kumen vos ven.

00:02:03.210 --> 00:02:05.810
nu, un ikh bin gegangen in kheyder un,

00:02:05.810 --> 00:02:09.040
der, di bekhurim zenen gekumen tsu mayne shvesters.

00:02:09.040 --> 00:02:11.940
tsvishn deye iz eyner geven, vi azoy me zogt, a

00:02:11.950 --> 00:02:16.210
a KADUR-REGEL, a a shpiler.

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:22.375
un der, gantsn tog fleg er, der nor, Tabak hot er geheysn, Tabak Emil.

00:02:22.510 --> 00:02:28.510
er iz geven a SHAR far a yidisher KVUTZA, azoy hot zi geheysn Shamshon.

00:02:29.100 --> 00:02:32.690
nu, der hot dem gantsn tog geklopt

00:02:32.700 --> 00:02:39.150
mit di mayses. mit dem KADUR-REGEL, mit vos ven, er fleg alts forn keyn Ungarn, oykhet fun dort oykh dertseylt,

00:02:39.380 --> 00:02:42.950
un ikh, alts yung yingl, vi me zogt, fleg ikh im kukn,

00:02:42.950 --> 00:02:45.730
in di oygn, vi azoy, vos a min er dertseylt.

00:02:45.920 --> 00:02:50.730
ober ikh hob dokh gebroykht geyn in kheyder, bin ikh gegangen in kheyder, vos ven.

00:02:50.730 --> 00:02:54.170
nu, ikh bin shoyn alt gevorn draytsn yor,

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:56.514
me hot dir gemakht a bar-mitsve?

00:02:56.479 --> 00:02:58.039
vi azoy? avade!

00:02:57.836 --> 00:02:59.552
vu iz er geven?

00:02:58.098 --> 00:02:58.872
in kheyder.

00:02:58.872 --> 00:03:00.066
in kheyder.

00:03:00.100 --> 00:03:10.280
dort hot men nisht gemakht azoyne bar-mitsves azoy vi do, deys hot men nor do gevoyr gevorn vi azoy me makht deys, un undzere shvegerin hot undz ge- dertseylt vi azoy de-...

00:03:02.797 --> 00:03:03.652
yo.

00:03:10.350 --> 00:03:12.760
ober dort iz geven in kheyder,

00:03:12.760 --> 00:03:17.440
gehat tfiln bakumen, un mit tfiln, geleygt tfiln, deys iz geven

00:03:17.490 --> 00:03:19.370
der gantser bar-mitsve

00:03:19.470 --> 00:03:22.772
un hostu nisht gehat keyn kesher mitn ABA?

00:03:23.100 --> 00:03:23.790
neyn.

00:03:24.009 --> 00:03:25.303
keyn shum kesher?

00:03:24.768 --> 00:03:25.129
nokh,

00:03:25.129 --> 00:03:27.870
eyn mol iz er nokh ongekumen keyn Siget,

00:03:28.160 --> 00:03:30.840
ven ikh bin shoyn geven azoy a greser yingl,

00:03:31.050 --> 00:03:35.130
nokh shpeter, nisht ven ikh bin shoyn nisht gegangen in kheyder nor a bisl greser,

00:03:35.270 --> 00:03:37.900
denstmol hot er gefregt

00:03:37.970 --> 00:03:41.200
di mame tsi zi lozt mikh az ikh zol geyn mit im.

00:03:41.200 --> 00:03:44.460
er zol mikh firn ahin. di mame hot nisht gevolt.

00:03:44.480 --> 00:03:45.470
zi nisht gelozt.

00:03:45.570 --> 00:03:50.820
vegn eyn eyntsik yingl, hot zi mikh nisht gelozt... un azoy, az er iz avek,

00:03:50.820 --> 00:03:54.140
un mer hob ikh fun im nisht gehert.

00:03:54.380 --> 00:03:57.390
er iz bayleyfik hingekumen

00:03:57.460 --> 00:03:59.450
in der Besarabye,

00:04:00.090 --> 00:04:01.110
vayl

00:04:01.110 --> 00:04:04.110
shpeter hot zikh dokh gemakht farshidene iberkerenishn,

00:04:04.110 --> 00:04:07.647
ahingekumen un fun im hob ikh mer nisht gevust.

00:04:07.690 --> 00:04:12.270
azoy az deys gantse iz undz geven farbindung mitn tate.

00:04:12.270 --> 00:04:15.170
ken men zogn az ikh bin oyfgevaksn onem

00:04:15.520 --> 00:04:17.843
tate, nor mit der mame.

00:04:18.630 --> 00:04:26.470
nu. ikh bin gegangen in kheyder, ikh hob gut gelernt, un der rebe hot zikh gegreyt fun mir tsu makhn a yeshive bokher.

00:04:26.470 --> 00:04:28.870
vi azoy me zogt, ikh zol geyn yeshive bokher.

00:04:29.400 --> 00:04:32.350
 bayn undz in shtub iz deys nisht geven

00:04:32.380 --> 00:04:33.740
azoyne problemen.

00:04:33.740 --> 00:04:38.640
undz ze'mir nisht geven keyn ikh veys vos a frume, ober nisht oysgeletste, vi azoy me zogt.

00:04:38.660 --> 00:04:42.890
 me hot gehaltn shabes, un me hot gehaltn kosher, di mame,

00:04:42.910 --> 00:04:46.080
un, di shvesters oykhet, vos ven.

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:52.140
un ikh biz vi lang ikh bin gegangen in kheyder, bin ikh oykh geven ales, vi azoy me zogt,

00:04:52.170 --> 00:04:54.700
oyfgefirt tsu mentshn,

00:04:54.820 --> 00:04:57.900
tsu mentshn un tsu layt, vi azoy me zogt, un tsu got,

00:04:57.990 --> 00:05:02.890
s'iz ales geven beseyder. ober mikh hot gepitshet az ikh bin dort alts farbundn,

00:05:02.890 --> 00:05:07.130
zuntik fleg ikh alts zen yeder loyft oyfn KADUR-REGEL,

00:05:07.180 --> 00:05:08.780
un ikh broykh geyn

00:05:08.879 --> 00:05:09.810
in kheyder.

00:05:09.877 --> 00:05:12.964
nu, ikh shmues mit mayn shvester,

00:05:12.964 --> 00:05:15.807
ikh vel geyn arbetn. me git mikh arayn

00:05:15.824 --> 00:05:17.561
alts lern yingl.

00:05:18.333 --> 00:05:20.350
in a shnayderay.

00:05:21.561 --> 00:05:26.017
nu, mayn shvester hot gehat ir bakante dort, geredt, geven a guter

00:05:26.017 --> 00:05:28.456
groyser shnayderay, azoy hot dos geheysn,

00:05:28.456 --> 00:05:31.228
Fisher Sholomon, der iz geven a bakanter

00:05:31.263 --> 00:05:32.596
froyen shnayder.

00:05:32.596 --> 00:05:38.496
dort gemakht froyen arbet, nisht kleyder far froyen, nor kostyumen, azoy...

00:05:38.148 --> 00:05:39.560
KHALIFOT.

00:05:38.933 --> 00:05:39.466
yo.

00:05:39.666 --> 00:05:41.859
kostyumen, mantlen, mit dos ven.

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:47.052
ahin bin ikh arayngegangen in toyznt nayn hundert dray in draysik.

00:05:47.368 --> 00:05:51.614
vi azoy me zogt, fraytik bin ikh avek funem kheyder,

00:05:51.842 --> 00:05:53.859
un montik tsu fri

00:05:53.859 --> 00:05:57.438
bin ikh arayn in der verk-shtub. un der rebe

00:05:57.754 --> 00:05:59.228
hot mikh nisht gezen.

00:06:00.017 --> 00:06:03.000
hot er mir bafoyln mit di kin-, mit di

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:06.614
mit di khaveyrim az ikh hob im zeyer opgefopt.

00:06:06.614 --> 00:06:09.543
er hot gerekhnt ikh vel zayn zayn a

00:06:09.614 --> 00:06:11.807
a yeshive bokher, un ikh

00:06:11.807 --> 00:06:12.754
bin avek.

00:06:12.842 --> 00:06:14.877
nu, ikh bin takn avek,

00:06:14.894 --> 00:06:17.754
me hot gebroykht lebn oykhet,

00:06:17.859 --> 00:06:19.789
nu, bay der

00:06:19.877 --> 00:06:21.729
hob ikh gearbet dort als

00:06:21.894 --> 00:06:23.877
lern yingl, bay der mishpokhe,

00:06:23.877 --> 00:06:26.438
bay dem shnayderay Fish- Fishle-,

00:06:26.631 --> 00:06:27.666
Fisher,

00:06:27.736 --> 00:06:31.508
un s'iz gegangen, dort s'iz geven mer, un dos ven. nu,

00:06:32.912 --> 00:06:35.385
nokh geven andere kinder, vos ven,

00:06:35.385 --> 00:06:37.000
bakant gemakht mit

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.736
undzere khevre lay,t

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:42.070
me geyen mir tsu der HANOAR HATZIONI.

00:06:42.070 --> 00:06:46.105
dos iz geven a organizatsye, a tsienistishe organizatsye,

00:06:46.280 --> 00:06:47.842
dey hot gehat,

00:06:47.842 --> 00:06:50.684
vi me zogt, a a shayer nisht a

00:06:50.684 --> 00:06:52.649
shtub, a plats.

00:06:52.649 --> 00:06:53.824
dort flegn zikh

00:06:53.912 --> 00:06:57.929
tsamkumen, shpetsyel shabes, ober oyf der nakht oykhet,

00:06:57.929 --> 00:07:02.087
iz geven bay Sholomonen, azoy hot geheysn, Sholomon der varger

00:07:02.087 --> 00:07:04.964
hot men im gerufn, dort in hoyf,

00:07:05.140 --> 00:07:08.228
zey, dort in hoyf iz geven der NOAR HATZION.

00:07:08.298 --> 00:07:10.035
nu, un mayn

00:07:10.035 --> 00:07:13.105
ROSH HAKVUTZA, vi azoy me hot denstmol gezogt,

00:07:13.105 --> 00:07:17.192
iz geven eyner Hilman Lazar, do voynt er in

00:07:17.263 --> 00:07:20.491
in Bat-Yam trefn mir zikh alts,

00:07:20.491 --> 00:07:24.122
shmuesn, er iz elter fun mir shoyn haynt akhtsik yor, ober,

00:07:24.122 --> 00:07:27.508
halt zikh gut. er iz gekumen shoyn fun lang do in land.

00:07:27.877 --> 00:07:31.087
un do hob ikh mikh getrofn dem dem,

00:07:31.087 --> 00:07:35.831
vi azoy me zogt, dem rosh fun der gantser HANOAR HATISONI, azoy hot er geheysn,

00:07:35.894 --> 00:07:39.912
Fuks, Fuks Ferents, Fuks Feri.

00:07:39.929 --> 00:07:42.666
far a yor, leyder iz er geshtorbn, er emes iz shoyn geven

00:07:42.666 --> 00:07:45.368
oykh bay dey, bay di yorn, vi azoy me zogt.

00:07:45.473 --> 00:07:51.192
nu, dort bin ikh gegangen, dort hot men, dort hob ikh dos ershte mol ongehoybn tsu hern fun di zakhn,

00:07:51.192 --> 00:07:57.368
Khaim Nakhmen Bialik iz geven, gedenk ikh, dos ershte fun velkhn mir hobn geredt. Nordoy, fun velkhn mir ho'mir ge-

00:07:57.456 --> 00:08:01.877
ge- getaynet in yene tsaytn, Khaim Veytsman hot denstmol geshpilt a role,

00:08:01.877 --> 00:08:03.421
nisht der Khaim Veytsman.

00:08:03.421 --> 00:08:04.754
zayn

00:08:05.017 --> 00:08:07.456
foter's bruder tsi, vi azoy UNK.

00:08:07.456 --> 00:08:08.789
yener Khaim Veytsman.

00:08:08.789 --> 00:08:12.052
hobn geshpilt denstmol a role in dey mayses.

00:08:12.052 --> 00:08:16.543
ikh shmues nisht fun Hertslen, Hertsl Tivodor fun velkhn me hot,

00:08:16.578 --> 00:08:25.368
oykh geredt, un di ale mayses. shoyn un deys iz ale, me hot gegangen, dort hot men gelernt zingen ivrit, hebreishe

00:08:25.368 --> 00:08:26.517
lider.

00:08:26.561 --> 00:08:30.052
un me hot getantst, vi azoy me zogt, hora,

00:08:30.052 --> 00:08:33.473
vi azoy a yingl, kinder, yunge yinglekh, yunge meydlekh,

00:08:33.473 --> 00:08:36.586
un se iz gegangen dort dos lebn,

00:08:37.580 --> 00:08:39.937
un fun Hitlern hostu gornisht gehert?

00:08:39.999 --> 00:08:46.596
ikh vel onkumen tsu Hitlern, ikh nem ales, vi azoy me zogt, in der in di reye.

00:08:46.736 --> 00:08:51.842
in toyznt nayn hundert finef un draysik,

00:08:52.017 --> 00:08:57.964
azoy vi ikh hob gearbet, iz geven a groyse SHVITA dort bayn undz in shtot, dort bay di shnayders.

00:08:58.035 --> 00:09:03.719
in shtot iz geven merere shnayderayen. bay dey shnayders iz geven a SHVITA.

00:09:04.000 --> 00:09:06.894
nu, azoy vi di SHVITA, hob ikh mikh oykhet,

00:09:06.894 --> 00:09:13.035
ken men aroysblaybn? emes ikh bin geven nor a lern yingl, ober ikh hob dokh nisht gekent UNK nor me hot nisht gearbet.

00:09:13.035 --> 00:09:15.105
nu, iz men avek tsum

00:09:15.122 --> 00:09:17.210
sindikat HISTRADUT.

00:09:17.210 --> 00:09:18.350
vi me zogt haynt.

00:09:18.350 --> 00:09:22.586
dort hot men ongehoybn tsu redn fun dem, fun yenem, farshidene mayses mit vos ven,

00:09:23.403 --> 00:09:28.561
un tsu bislekh, tsu bislekh hob ikh ongehoybn tsu geyn

00:09:28.614 --> 00:09:31.210
nisht tsu der NOAR HATZIONI,

00:09:31.245 --> 00:09:33.456
nor tsum sindikat.

00:09:33.543 --> 00:09:37.280
in sindikat iz geven dort a guter biblyotek.

00:09:37.649 --> 00:09:41.912
un mir sh- ikh hob lib gehat tsu, shoyn ikh vel onkumen tsu dem oykh.

00:09:42.018 --> 00:09:43.561
un, dort hot men

00:09:42.860 --> 00:09:44.123
vos hostu lib gehat?

00:09:44.105 --> 00:09:46.473
tsu lezn zeyer gut.

00:09:46.473 --> 00:09:48.701
un dort hot men geshpilt shakh.

00:09:48.859 --> 00:09:50.666
dort hot men geshpilt shakh.

00:09:50.684 --> 00:09:53.193
dort iz geven a a

00:09:53.193 --> 00:09:55.473
a a zingen

00:09:55.473 --> 00:10:02.754
khor, vi azoy me zogt, m- zingen, MAKHELA, vos me zingt, dort gekumen a lerer a profesor,

00:09:56.876 --> 00:09:58.406
MAKHELA, MAKHELA.

00:10:02.807 --> 00:10:08.789
mit a fidl, mit dos ven, un me hot dortn gezungen, vos ven, deys iz, s'iz gefeln, me iz aropgegangen

00:10:08.789 --> 00:10:11.912
far nakhts, me hot nisht gehat vos tsu tun, iz men aropgegangen ahin.

00:10:11.912 --> 00:10:13.912
un dort hot men getun

00:10:14.122 --> 00:10:16.947
vos, fun di ale zakhn.

00:10:16.982 --> 00:10:18.649
nu, azoy bin ikh dort

00:10:18.684 --> 00:10:20.315
geblibn. in di tsayt

00:10:20.403 --> 00:10:24.894
iz dort geven eyner an advokat, azoy hot er geheysn Kotsnadi.

00:10:24.964 --> 00:10:28.209
vegn dem zog ikh dem nomen, vayl er iz geven, vi azoy me zogt, mayn ershter

00:10:28.473 --> 00:10:32.298
velkher mikh in di zakhn arayngefirt,

00:10:32.578 --> 00:10:36.403
un er hot undz avekgefirt shpiln KADUR-YAD,

00:10:36.403 --> 00:10:43.807
shpiln KADUR-REGEL, der iz geven an advokat, nor er hot gezen az s'iz oreme yinglekh, un shnayder yinglekh, shuster yinglekh,

00:10:43.824 --> 00:10:47.649
mit ikh veys vos a min, hot er zey aroysgefirt oyfn

00:10:47.684 --> 00:10:50.684
oyfn, nu, oyfn

00:10:50.701 --> 00:10:52.736
oyf di SHTICHIM, un dort

00:10:52.771 --> 00:10:55.543
geshpilt un ge- m- ge-.

00:10:56.087 --> 00:11:04.245
nu, un dort gelernt, dos ershte bukh, tsum bayshpil, vos ikh hob fun dort aroysgenumen, funem sindikat gedenk ikh azoy vi haynt iz geven

00:11:04.245 --> 00:11:06.228
dem UPTON SINCLAIR,

00:11:06.228 --> 00:11:08.666
der Amerikaner shrayber,

00:11:09.543 --> 00:11:12.456
Amerikaner shrayber UPTON SINCLAIR,

00:11:12.508 --> 00:11:13.421
er hot gehat,

00:11:13.456 --> 00:11:16.719
CHICAGO, azoy hot deys geheysn. bashraybt er dort

00:11:17.000 --> 00:11:22.210
di gefl- di fa- di fleysh, di, vi azoy zogt men shoyn? di,

00:11:22.543 --> 00:11:26.508
vi me shekht di hiner mit di beheymes, nu, di

00:11:26.543 --> 00:11:28.719
fleysh fleysh brik.

00:11:28.736 --> 00:11:30.140
fleysh brik yo.

00:11:30.140 --> 00:11:33.000
vu me shekht di beheymes, un vos ven. dort fleg men shekhtn

00:11:33.070 --> 00:11:36.814
toyznter un hunderter toyznter beheymes, vos ven, hot er dort aropgeshribn

00:11:36.894 --> 00:11:41.280
vos a min shver lebn yene hobn dort, un dos deys gantse lebn.

00:11:41.350 --> 00:11:42.736
deys hot mir,

00:11:43.070 --> 00:11:46.228
vi azoy me zogt, zeyer gefeln.

00:11:46.385 --> 00:11:48.596
hot mikh arayngefirt in a nayer velt.

00:11:48.849 --> 00:11:50.105
UNK hot er

00:11:50.122 --> 00:11:53.456
PETROLEUM, azoy heyst es, nokh petrol, nokh,

00:11:53.491 --> 00:11:57.526
oykhet aza bikhl, oykhet fun di problemen, vi azoy,

00:11:57.526 --> 00:12:00.035
vi azoy me hot gelebt, un vi azoy me hot dort getun.

00:12:00.035 --> 00:12:04.035
un fun dem UPTON SINCLAIRn hob ikh genumen, vi azoy me zogt, esn.

00:12:04.157 --> 00:12:06.912
deye bikher, dey z mir gefeln.

00:12:07.245 --> 00:12:10.508
nokh dem, ikh bin shoyn aribergegangen oyf andere, tsum bayshpil

00:12:10.543 --> 00:12:13.982
STEFAN ZWEIG, iz geven denstmol yene di mode,

00:12:14.017 --> 00:12:16.421
 HEINRICH MANN,

00:12:16.421 --> 00:12:22.842
HEINRICH MANN iz nisht geven mit azoyne problemen, ober er iz geven oykhet mit humanishe problemen.

00:12:22.964 --> 00:12:23.842
demolts geven

00:12:23.877 --> 00:12:25.438
STEFAN HEIM,

00:12:25.456 --> 00:12:28.245
hot gehat, tsum bayshpil, azoy gedenk ikh haynt, a bikhl,

00:12:28.245 --> 00:12:29.719
"ikh bin hungerik."

00:12:29.719 --> 00:12:31.298
azoy hot es geheysn.

00:12:31.438 --> 00:12:35.315
un deys iz mir oykh zeyer gefeln, un vos ven.

00:12:35.315 --> 00:12:38.157
nu, azoy bin ikh tsu bislekh

00:12:38.157 --> 00:12:40.210
arayngegangen, azoy vi me zogt,

00:12:40.210 --> 00:12:45.491
fun fun fun MERKAZ, fun CENTRU oyf links.

00:12:45.491 --> 00:12:47.333
oyf der linker zayt.

00:12:48.964 --> 00:12:53.473
un dort iz nokh geven eyner,

00:12:53.543 --> 00:12:58.807
se dort ahin flegn kumen merere yinglekh, un vos ven, iz geven in undzer shtot

00:12:58.807 --> 00:13:06.035
a yin-, familyes, mer mit azoyne linke linke khev- gevezene yeshive bokherim.

00:13:06.070 --> 00:13:11.157
gevezene farshidene, zey zenen araynge-, aribergegangen oyf der linker zayt.

00:13:11.245 --> 00:13:14.614
iz geven eyner Khaim Morkovitsh.

00:13:14.824 --> 00:13:18.526
dey mishpokhe iz geven a a khasidishe mishpokhe.

00:13:18.526 --> 00:13:23.578
der foter, mit a bord, di muter mit a sheytl, mit alem, vos ven,

00:13:23.666 --> 00:13:27.298
un der Khaim Morkovitsh iz geven a inteligenter

00:13:27.298 --> 00:13:31.245
mentsh, a inteligenter bokher, oykh geven koydem a yeshive bokher,

00:13:31.438 --> 00:13:37.263
un der iz gevorn shoyn hot farfirt far a yidishe lererke, vi azoy me zogt,

00:13:37.298 --> 00:13:38.325
Hartman,

00:13:38.333 --> 00:13:42.035
Harmot, Hormot Leye, azoy hot zi geheysn Hormot Lili,

00:13:42.526 --> 00:13:44.631
un der

00:13:44.631 --> 00:13:48.193
hot undz gezen azoy, vi azoy undz lezn mir, undz geyen mir,

00:13:48.193 --> 00:13:51.140
hot er a por yinglekh avekgerufn,

00:13:51.228 --> 00:13:53.473
zoln mir geyn oyf a trefung

00:13:53.473 --> 00:13:55.368
ahin un ahin. dos iz geven

00:13:55.368 --> 00:13:59.491
in der shu- in der shul, in der kheyder fun kool.

00:13:59.491 --> 00:14:02.771
in kool's khadorim, azoy hot men geheysn dort in Siget.

00:14:03.157 --> 00:14:06.298
un oyf der nakht ze'mir undz ahin ongekumen,

00:14:06.298 --> 00:14:08.561
se geven tunkl. me hot nisht gezen,

00:14:08.561 --> 00:14:11.193
nisht getort se zol zayn likhtik.

00:14:11.403 --> 00:14:14.105
un dort hot men undz ongehoybn tsu redn, fun

00:14:14.105 --> 00:14:17.824
farshidene shverikeytn vos di arbayter

00:14:18.035 --> 00:14:19.508
geyen durkh,

00:14:19.894 --> 00:14:23.385
un deys iz der shuld avade di velts

00:14:23.385 --> 00:14:25.333
borg- kapitalistn,

00:14:25.333 --> 00:14:28.807
mit azoyne zakhn. un s'iz do

00:14:28.807 --> 00:14:30.842
a komunistishe partey.

00:14:30.842 --> 00:14:34.526
velkhe zi hot gemakht a nay land, un deys land,

00:14:34.526 --> 00:14:38.894
deys zog ikh nor azoy in groysn az

00:14:37.828 --> 00:14:39.071
BEKITZUR.

00:14:38.894 --> 00:14:41.000
azoy vi me zogt, oyfn alef beys

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:42.346
durkh mit di ale problemen.

00:14:42.473 --> 00:14:45.245
nu, un azoy hob ikh ongehoybn,

00:14:45.245 --> 00:14:47.421
fleg men undz alts yede vokh

00:14:47.473 --> 00:14:49.421
hobn aza trefung,

00:14:49.456 --> 00:14:55.561
un oyf der trefung, fleg men alts farshidene probl- interesante zakhn vos mikh alts yung yingl,

00:14:55.578 --> 00:14:59.140
un vos ikh hob nisht gekent, ikh bin nisht gegangen in groyse shuln,

00:14:59.140 --> 00:15:01.456
hot mikh interesirt di ale zakhn.

00:15:02.142 --> 00:15:04.959
un in Siget iz nokh geven

00:15:04.959 --> 00:15:07.000
a biblyotek

00:15:07.000 --> 00:15:09.897
vos iz geven groshn bikhlekh.

00:15:09.959 --> 00:15:13.612
azoy hot men deys ongerufn, far vos hot es geheysn groshn bikhlekh? oyf yidish.

00:15:13.673 --> 00:15:16.693
yidish. vayl zey zenen geven fun Poyln,

00:15:16.693 --> 00:15:21.571
un zey zenen geven zeyer bilik, un in Poyln iz geven gelt, groshn.

00:15:21.612 --> 00:15:24.471
un deys, zog men, far a groshn ken men bakumen aza,

00:15:24.510 --> 00:15:28.469
hot men gekent farshafn aza bikhl, hot dos geheysn groshn bikhlekh.

00:15:28.571 --> 00:15:33.489
un di groshn bikhlekh, deys iz geven, azoy rekhn ikh, funem bund.

00:15:33.489 --> 00:15:36.530
der bund iz oykh geven a groyse fareyn in

00:15:36.530 --> 00:15:38.449
Poyln, a linke fareyn.

00:15:38.693 --> 00:15:43.163
nu, un di bikhlekh hot men bashribn. tsum bayshpil azoy vi haynt gedenk ikh,

00:15:43.183 --> 00:15:44.319
ikh heyb nisht fun,

00:15:44.326 --> 00:15:48.265
Sverdlovskn, iz geven eyner tsvishn di ershte firer in Rusland,

00:15:48.265 --> 00:15:49.836
Trotskin,

00:15:49.836 --> 00:15:52.489
 velkhe zenen nokh geven?

00:15:52.510 --> 00:15:55.183
Bukharin,

00:15:55.183 --> 00:15:56.836
zenen geven di ale,

00:15:56.836 --> 00:16:06.367
 ikh shmues nisht fun Stalinen, un fun Leninen, un fun dey ale, fun Marksn, fun dey ale, dey ale hobn gehat ekstere ekstere bikhlekh, s'iz nisht geven keyn groyse bikhlekh,

00:16:06.367 --> 00:16:07.816
azoy dine bikhlekh,

00:16:07.816 --> 00:16:10.489
un dey hobn bashribn zeyer lebn,

00:16:10.489 --> 00:16:15.449
un tsum sof, iz nokh geven, vi azoy me zogt, aza velts problem, tsum bayshpil,

00:16:15.449 --> 00:16:17.183
vos iz der

00:16:17.183 --> 00:16:20.755
der Suezer? der Suezer durkhgang, do bay Mitsrayim,

00:16:20.755 --> 00:16:23.224
der Suez iz geven denstmol a groyse zakh,

00:16:23.285 --> 00:16:25.877
tsi vos iz der Gibralter, vos heyst deys?

00:16:25.877 --> 00:16:27.040
tsi,

00:16:27.040 --> 00:16:30.346
ikh veys vos, tsi, azoyne

00:16:30.411 --> 00:16:31.959
farshidene zakhn,

00:16:31.959 --> 00:16:35.510
deys hot undz gefeln, un tsu bislekh, tsu bislekh

00:16:35.571 --> 00:16:38.469
ze'mir arayngegangen in deye

00:16:38.469 --> 00:16:39.571
problemen,

00:16:39.571 --> 00:16:43.408
un ikh hob vayter gearbet, zelbst farshtendlekh,

00:16:44.224 --> 00:16:47.612
un gegangen in sindikat.

00:16:48.469 --> 00:16:53.816
un, vi azoy me zogt, der Khaim Morkovitsh hot gezogt, "nu,

00:16:54.142 --> 00:16:56.040
fun hitst mol on

00:16:56.040 --> 00:17:01.795
vet zikh mit dir, mit aykh, vi azoy me zogt, bafasn, nisht ikh

00:17:01.918 --> 00:17:05.204
vet zikh bafasn mit dir an anderer.

00:17:06.591 --> 00:17:09.632
vet zikh bafasn mit dir an anderer."

00:17:10.102 --> 00:17:12.510
un der hot geheysn

00:17:12.632 --> 00:17:14.775
Fogel Avromi.

00:17:14.979 --> 00:17:20.653
der Fogel Avromi iz nisht fun lang tsurikgekumen fun der tfise.

00:17:20.653 --> 00:17:22.836
vu er iz opgezesn finef yor,

00:17:22.836 --> 00:17:27.489
in di, a shvere tfise in Rumenye, DOFTANA, azoy hot es geheysn.

00:17:27.979 --> 00:17:33.775
un der, vi azoy me zogt, iz dokh shoyn geven a emesdiker komunist. nu,

00:17:33.918 --> 00:17:37.408
der hot undz afirgenumen, un

00:17:37.571 --> 00:17:45.622
me hot shoyn geredt fun dem, az me broykh nokh farshafn andere yinglekh, un nokh kumen, ahin aher,

00:17:45.673 --> 00:17:50.326
un nokh a tsayt, hot men gezogt, "nu, Hershl,

00:17:50.346 --> 00:17:53.693
du geyst ariber itster tsu TOMASH

00:17:53.693 --> 00:17:56.122
SANYI. se iz geven an unger,

00:17:56.224 --> 00:17:57.632
der iz geven,

00:17:57.632 --> 00:18:01.356
vi azoy me zogt, in undzer gegnt der hoypt fun di komunistn.

00:18:02.449 --> 00:18:05.918
TOMASH. iber gants Maramoresh denstmol.

00:18:05.918 --> 00:18:09.040
er iz geven a unger, a tishler,

00:18:09.040 --> 00:18:12.795
far mir geven a voyler bokher, vi azoy me zogt, un a

00:18:12.795 --> 00:18:16.449
geven a guter, a gelernter bokher, azoy vos ven,

00:18:16.469 --> 00:18:17.755
un

00:18:17.755 --> 00:18:22.857
azoy, ikh bin gegangen, gelernt, un me hot gearbet, un hob dort

00:18:22.877 --> 00:18:26.224
zikh getrofn, nokh mentshn, nokh yinglekh,

00:18:26.387 --> 00:18:31.775
un a tsayt hot men gezogt, "nu, itst broykh men manifestn

00:18:31.836 --> 00:18:36.551
tseshpreytn." in Rumenye iz dokh geven farbotn di komunistishe partey.

00:18:36.551 --> 00:18:39.420
dort iz gekumen tfise far azoyne zakhn.

00:18:40.204 --> 00:18:44.653
un ho'mir bakumen azoyne manifestn,

00:18:44.816 --> 00:18:47.571
un ikh hob organizirt

00:18:47.755 --> 00:18:51.224
vu me zol geyn, tsu tsvey yinglekh,

00:18:51.387 --> 00:18:54.285
zoln geyn oyf der nakht, iz deys geven,

00:18:55.040 --> 00:19:01.612
un avek iz men avek fun Lenger shul, dort iz geven der der opmakh, vi azoy me zogt,

00:19:01.736 --> 00:19:02.709
MERKAZ.

00:19:02.510 --> 00:19:07.306
yo. un m'iz gegangen un me hot tseshpreyt deye zakhn.

00:19:07.428 --> 00:19:09.224
ikh, gedenk ikh azoy vi haynt,

00:19:09.224 --> 00:19:11.244
se hot mir zeyer vey getun di tseyn,

00:19:11.387 --> 00:19:14.428
bin ikh avekgegangen tsun a tseyn dokter vos mayn

00:19:14.428 --> 00:19:19.551
shvesters a bakante, zi hot gehat merer bakante, zi iz geven aza meydl, zi iz geven a sheyn meydl, un iz zi geven aza

00:19:19.551 --> 00:19:22.265
lebedike moyd, vi azoy me zogt, yo.

00:19:22.367 --> 00:19:26.574
un ikh bin aribergegangen tsu dem tseyn dokter, un fun dort, dos iz geven oyf a shtok,

00:19:26.714 --> 00:19:28.591
un fun dort hob ikh gezen

00:19:28.632 --> 00:19:31.163
vi di MISHTARA, di politsey,

00:19:31.163 --> 00:19:34.326
me rukt, me geyt, me kukt mit dos ven,

00:19:34.551 --> 00:19:39.469
vos hot pasirt? "me hot gevorfn komunistishe manifestn dey nakht!"

00:19:39.469 --> 00:19:44.673
hot men geredt in shtot., nu, ikh hob deys gekukt.

00:19:43.350 --> 00:19:45.437
ven iz dos geven, velkhe yor?

00:19:45.122 --> 00:19:48.673
deys iz geven in toyznt nayn hundert

00:19:49.000 --> 00:19:51.142
akht un draysik.

00:19:51.142 --> 00:19:53.795
ikh bin shoyn geven a yingl fun nayntsn yor.

00:19:54.040 --> 00:19:56.979
akhts un draysik, bayleyfik, yo.

00:19:57.040 --> 00:19:59.346
zibenem un draysik, akht un draysik.

00:19:59.408 --> 00:20:03.367
mit dem gantsn sindikat, hob ikh obgehoybn mit toyznt nayn hundert

00:20:03.469 --> 00:20:06.918
zeks un draysik. un denstmol bin ikh shoyn geven, vi azoy me zogt,

00:20:07.142 --> 00:20:09.346
arayngegesn in deye

00:20:09.428 --> 00:20:11.489
ale zakhn.

00:20:11.673 --> 00:20:13.020
un azoy hob ikh alts

00:20:13.020 --> 00:20:15.122
vayter un vayter gegangen.

00:20:16.571 --> 00:20:17.260
nu...

00:20:17.266 --> 00:20:19.288
vos hostu gevust fun Hitlern?

00:20:18.432 --> 00:20:20.567
m-, fun Hitlern

00:20:20.567 --> 00:20:22.540
hob ikh gevust, vi azoy me zogt,

00:20:22.540 --> 00:20:24.918
ales un, vi azoy me zogt,

00:20:24.918 --> 00:20:26.918
ikh hob gelezt, koydem

00:20:27.054 --> 00:20:30.459
iz dokh geven fun zey der broyner,

00:20:31.270 --> 00:20:33.594
oyf ungerish a BARNA,

00:20:33.621 --> 00:20:36.837
a BARNA KONYV, s'iz geven a

00:20:36.837 --> 00:20:39.432
b- broyner, broyner bukh,

00:20:39.432 --> 00:20:41.837
iz geven aroysgegebn in yene tsaytn

00:20:41.837 --> 00:20:44.054
fun der antifashistishe

00:20:44.216 --> 00:20:47.567
bavegung, nisht nor fun Rumenye, ikh meyn der velt,

00:20:47.567 --> 00:20:51.432
hot men aroysgegebn iber di gesheenishn vos se tut zikh op in

00:20:51.567 --> 00:20:52.685
Daytshland.

00:20:51.575 --> 00:20:52.666
Daytshland.

00:20:53.333 --> 00:20:57.333
un dort hot men

00:20:57.333 --> 00:21:04.500
ongehoybn iber dem shoyn tsu redn, iber dey iber, vi azoy me zogt, der antviklung funem fashizm.

00:21:04.500 --> 00:21:08.233
azoy iz es geven. vayl denstmol iz shoyn geven nisht nor

00:21:08.233 --> 00:21:12.400
Daytshland mit Hitlern, nor s'iz geven Musolini mit

00:21:12.400 --> 00:21:14.000
mit Italye.

00:21:14.000 --> 00:21:20.666
un zey, azoy vi Musolini hot ongehoybn di ershte krig mit Abisinye, mitn hayntikn Etiopye,

00:21:20.733 --> 00:21:24.466
iz der Negus iz gevorn a held vayl er hot zikh akegn geshtelt,

00:21:24.466 --> 00:21:27.766
iz deys geven a problem fun tsu redn,

00:21:27.866 --> 00:21:30.566
un iber dem hot men geredt, un iber dem hot men getaynet,

00:21:30.566 --> 00:21:34.433
un iber Daytshland ho'mir hob ikh dokh gevust,

00:21:34.500 --> 00:21:38.700
un koydem iz dokh gekumen di ale politishe

00:21:38.700 --> 00:21:43.066
problemen vos di England un Frankraykh hobn alts prubirt

00:21:43.100 --> 00:21:45.333
tsu shtiln di velt,

00:21:45.333 --> 00:21:49.733
az Hitler vet nisht arayngeyn in a velts-krig, az er vet nisht

00:21:49.733 --> 00:21:54.100
ongrayfn andere felker, un vos ven, me hot mit im gemakht a f-

00:21:54.100 --> 00:21:55.751
a far-, a farmakh,

00:21:55.800 --> 00:21:58.633
tsum bayshpil mit, az er vet nisht ongrayfn Tshekh-,

00:21:59.466 --> 00:22:01.233
Tshekhoslovakay,

00:22:01.300 --> 00:22:05.566
er vet nisht ongrayfn Poyln, hot men mit im gemakht a faraynshtandung, ales UNK.

00:22:03.227 --> 00:22:03.829
yo.

