vos iz demolt geven?

00:22:12.710 --> 00:22:13.649
far...

00:22:13.785 --> 00:22:14.231
yo.

00:22:14.800 --> 00:22:20.500
 in der tsayt iz shoyn mayn, di groyse shvester shoyn,

00:22:20.500 --> 00:22:24.800
vi azoy me zogt, tsu zikh gekumen, zi iz shoyn gezunt gevorn,

00:22:24.800 --> 00:22:29.700
di klenere shvester iz oykhet arayngegangen arbetn in a,

00:22:29.700 --> 00:22:33.766
azoy hot es geheysn, Shtern Nandor, deys iz geven a yidishe fabrik,

00:22:33.766 --> 00:22:36.566
oykhet a shtriker shtriker fabrik,

