00:24:17.730 --> 00:24:22.038
un deys iz gevorn bazetst, vi me zogt, fun di ungerishe fashistn.

00:24:22.307 --> 00:24:25.807
un in der tsayt, un befor mit a yor,

00:24:25.923 --> 00:24:29.499
hot Daytshland bazetst Tshekhoslovakay,

00:24:29.499 --> 00:24:34.384
Moravia un yene gegnt, azoy az Tshekhoslovakay iz shoyn geven

00:24:34.461 --> 00:24:38.038
denstmol in gantsn tsu grunt geshtelt.

00:24:38.192 --> 00:24:42.026
un deys iz geven in toyznt nayn hundert naynem un draysik.

00:24:42.076 --> 00:24:44.423
nu, azoy hot men dort

00:24:44.723 --> 00:24:45.511
vayter gelebt.

00:24:45.769 --> 00:24:47.690
dervayl,

00:24:47.889 --> 00:24:50.970
di velts politik hot dokh undz nisht gelozt ruen,

00:24:50.970 --> 00:24:52.794
se iz dokh gegangen vayter,

00:24:53.000 --> 00:24:57.264
hobn zey, di Ungern ongehoybn tsu betn

00:24:57.411 --> 00:25:00.794
Transilvanye, s'iz geven di gegnt vu undz ho'mir

00:25:00.911 --> 00:25:02.852
gevoynt, Rumenye.

00:25:02.852 --> 00:25:05.147
oyf ungerish heyst es

00:25:05.235 --> 00:25:08.058
ERDELY, un oyf yidish hot men gezogt

00:25:08.058 --> 00:25:09.500
Transilvanye.

00:25:09.735 --> 00:25:16.382
hobn di di ungern deys gebetn. un oyf dem hot men ongehoybn zikh tsu taynen mit hin aher, mit

00:25:16.411 --> 00:25:19.235
Musolini, mit Hitlern fun eyn zayt,

00:25:19.235 --> 00:25:23.147
CHAMBERLAIN mit DALADIER, yene zenen geven denstmol bay di englender,

00:25:23.147 --> 00:25:25.882
CHAMBERLAIN, un bay di frantsoyzer DALADIER,

00:25:25.911 --> 00:25:27.382
fun der anderer zayt,

00:25:27.382 --> 00:25:31.558
di day- di daytshn mit di Ungern hobn alts tsugezogt, dey hobn azoy gezogt,

00:25:31.558 --> 00:25:35.000
azoy az in toyznt nayn hundert fertsik,

00:25:35.117 --> 00:25:36.852
in september,

00:25:36.852 --> 00:25:39.529
hot men zikh tsamgetrofn in Vin,

00:25:39.529 --> 00:25:41.176
dey ale firers,

00:25:41.294 --> 00:25:45.588
un me hot bashtetikt az deys geyt ariber tsu Ungern.

00:25:45.588 --> 00:25:48.147
dos heyst undz, vu mir ho'mir gevoynt,

00:25:48.147 --> 00:25:52.588
az undzer zayt geyt ariber tsu Ungern. oys Rumenye,

00:25:52.588 --> 00:25:54.235
di rumenishe armey

00:25:54.235 --> 00:25:56.147
hot zikh tsurikgetsoygn,

00:25:56.243 --> 00:25:58.235
un undz ze'mir gevorn Ungern.

00:25:58.262 --> 00:26:00.669
un se iz geven epes a

00:26:00.877 --> 00:26:03.119
andere situatsye?

00:26:03.119 --> 00:26:03.825
fun

00:26:03.915 --> 00:26:06.355
esn, se iz geven arbet, se iz geven esn?

00:26:06.275 --> 00:26:09.559
esn iz geven ales. di, azoy fun, oyf...

00:26:08.975 --> 00:26:11.150
s'iz nisht geven keyn UNK.

00:26:09.559 --> 00:26:13.974
oyf der oyvn hot zikh nisht geshpirt gornisht, in di ershte yorn.

00:26:14.029 --> 00:26:15.941
keyn shum problemen, di Ungern...

00:26:15.941 --> 00:26:19.558
far vos? vayl deys iz dokh geven befor oykhet Ungern.

00:26:19.558 --> 00:26:21.764
in toyznt nayn hundert akhtsn,

00:26:21.764 --> 00:26:25.000
iz deys oykh geven Ungern.

00:26:22.832 --> 00:26:23.546
yo.

00:26:23.557 --> 00:26:26.606
un ven, ven es iz gevorn tsores?

00:26:26.676 --> 00:26:29.500
di tsores hobn zikh ongehoybn

00:26:29.500 --> 00:26:33.617
nokh dem vi ikh bin shoyn avek, do vel ikh tsukumen vi ikh bin shoyn...

00:26:33.617 --> 00:26:36.117
in toyznt nayn hundert

00:26:36.205 --> 00:26:42.352
dray un fertsik, ober in fir un fertsik, denstmol iz shoyn geven, vi azoy me zogt, fartik. ober...

00:26:41.225 --> 00:26:43.433
vos gedenkstu fun dem?

00:26:42.382 --> 00:26:44.735
biz do, biz do,

00:26:44.849 --> 00:26:47.058
hob ikh nokh durkhgelebt shvere

00:26:47.088 --> 00:26:49.029
tsaytn, ikh,

00:26:49.117 --> 00:26:53.470
vi di ungern zenen arayngekumen, toyznt nayn hundert fertsik,

00:26:53.470 --> 00:26:56.529
zenen zey arayngekumen mit zeyer gantser politik.

00:26:56.529 --> 00:26:58.676
zeyer fashistishe politik.

00:26:58.794 --> 00:27:00.852
un, vi azoy me zogt,

00:27:00.882 --> 00:27:04.466
a shverer antikomunistisher mayses.

00:27:04.500 --> 00:27:07.176
zey hobn dos ershte

00:27:07.176 --> 00:27:09.500
gezukht komunistn,

00:27:09.500 --> 00:27:11.911
vi vos iz do,

00:27:11.911 --> 00:27:14.176
yidn vos zey hern,

00:27:14.264 --> 00:27:16.852
me hot gehert dem radyo LONDRA.

00:27:16.882 --> 00:27:19.203
denstmol, dos iz geven antifashistishe...

00:27:18.502 --> 00:27:19.053
..

00:27:19.205 --> 00:27:21.147
hern un vos ven,

00:27:21.147 --> 00:27:24.323
un me hot ongehoybn tsamtsukhapn

00:27:24.382 --> 00:27:29.392
deye mentshn, ober deys iz nor geven, vi azoy me zogt, fun der oyvn.

00:27:29.083 --> 00:27:30.529
vos iz geven mit dir?

00:27:31.029 --> 00:27:32.288
mit mir,

00:27:34.318 --> 00:27:36.818
in toyznt nayn hundert

00:27:36.818 --> 00:27:40.409
eynem un fertsik, ven se hot oysgebrokhn di milkhome mit Rusnland,

00:27:40.409 --> 00:27:42.772
in tsvey un tsvantsikstn yuni,

00:27:42.909 --> 00:27:47.136
hot men mikh ayngerufn tsum arbets,

00:27:47.136 --> 00:27:50.909
di yidishe yinglekh hot men nisht gefirt in der armey,

00:27:50.909 --> 00:27:57.045
nisht in der TZAVA, nor shtots tsu der TZAVA, hot men gefirt in azoyne arbayts,

00:27:57.045 --> 00:28:00.318
 eyn-, eynheytn,

00:28:00.409 --> 00:28:04.272
arbayts detashamentn, azoy hot dos geheysn.

00:28:04.272 --> 00:28:12.090
ahin hot men undz avekgefirt, di Ungern, hot men mikh avekgefirt keyn, koydem keyn,

00:28:12.181 --> 00:28:20.818
keyn Munkatsh, deys iz oykh geven a shtot oyf yene zayt, dort geven groyse kazarmes, groyse militers,

00:28:20.818 --> 00:28:27.000
fun Ungern, vos ven, dort hot men undz geshtelt arbetn. me ho'mir gearbet, gefirt

00:28:27.000 --> 00:28:33.318
oyslodenen vagonen, fun der, fun der RAKEVET,

00:28:33.363 --> 00:28:38.318
 ongefirt in di, in di kazarmes bay der armey

00:28:38.318 --> 00:28:43.590
trogn mu- munitsyes, gevern, shlepn ahin un aher...

00:28:43.590 --> 00:28:50.227
dort bin ikh geven, un undz ho'mir gezen in a, dort iz geven aza mil.

00:28:50.227 --> 00:28:53.772
a mil vos a mol iz geven a yidishe mul- mil.
